      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/uq/monte-carlo-wear-volume-2024",
      "description": "FE-predicted cumulative wear volume at 5 Mc compared against three physical knee wear simulator runs (ISO 14243-1). Mean predicted wear: 42.3 mm³; mean experimental: 44.1 mm³; relative error 4.1%. 95% prediction interval from Monte Carlo UQ (n=1000 samples, material property and load magnitude inputs varied) spans 38.1–47.2 mm³, fully enclosing experimental mean. Validation metric: normalized root-mean-square error (NRMSE) = 0.061, satisfying acceptance criterion of NRMSE ≤ 0.10."
    },
