      "rationale": "Abaqus 2022 is a commercially validated FE code with published verification documentation. The in-house UMAT wear subroutine has been verified against published analytical wear solutions (Archard model, simple pin-on-disc geometry) with errors < 2%. SQA plan documented per ISO 9001 quality management system."
