        "description": "Nonlinear solver convergence criterion: force residual norm < 1×10⁻⁵ N for all load increments. Energy balance error (external work vs. internal strain energy + dissipation) < 0.1% per cycle. Contact penetration < 1 µm at converged solution. All criteria documented in solver output logs. Achieved Level 2 reflects standard convergence monitoring for commercial FE code."
      },
      "rationale": "All production simulations converged within 15 iterations per load increment with force residual < 1×10⁻⁵ N. Energy balance error ranged 0.02–0.07% across all simulated cycles. No contact penetration violations detected. Solver logs archived in project repository."
