        "description": "Minimum three tibial insert specimens from the same production lot and sterilization batch used in physical wear simulator validation. Specimen dimensional inspection confirms conformance to design nominal within ±0.05 mm. Pre-test surface roughness measured and documented. Achieved Level 2 reflects n=3 specimens with documented lot traceability and dimensional inspection."
      },
      "rationale": "Three tibial insert specimens (Lot 2023-TKR-07, gamma irradiated in N₂) used in ISO 14243-1 wear simulator test. Dimensional inspection: all within ±0.03 mm of nominal. Pre-test Ra: 0.41–0.44 µm (within UHMWPE machined surface specification). Lot traceability documented in test report TR-2024-03."
